relation: Joel Hanrahan starts the inning for the Nationals.
Pinch-Hitter Jason Michaels singled to left. Runner on first with none out and Miguel Tejada due up.
Miguel Tejada lined into a double play, second to first. None on with two outs and Hunter Pence due up.
Hunter Pence singled to center. Runner on first with two outs and Ivan Rodriguez due up.

Ivan Rodriguez reached first on an infield single to second. On the play, Hunter Pence advanced to third and Rodriguez advanced to second on Ronnie Belliard's throwing error. Runners on second and third with two outs and Geoff Blum due up.
Geoff Blum struck out swinging to end the inning.
